nodes.bodyText:
Oh, such a silly mistake!
Could we then replace the first call to getItemIndex with contains:
        if (!contains(targetItemIndex, dataProvider)) {
            throw new IllegalArgumentException(targetItemNotFoundErrorMessage);
        }

It's easier to read.

